{"tid":655108,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無人機拍礦區　遭河北戰機攔截","createTime":"2018-05-06T08:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T09:25:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e080d4df4c0c9b9bf1bc8de2b7ddfac07961dbea","tid":655108,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:23:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180506/20382466?_ga=2.73458002.1769260499.1525579676-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180506%2F20382466%3F_ga%3D2.73458002.1769260499.1525579676-581282530.1504247435&d=YAZ%2BkElEEF8wD3E%2BJLjm8PM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=eeb78ae3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180506%2F20382466%3F_ga%3D2.73458002.1769260499.1525579676-581282530.1504247435&h=37f8366a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180506/20382466?_ga=2.73458002.1769260499.1525579676-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月06日 <br />\n<br />\n無人機拍礦區　遭河北戰機攔截<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180506/large/a1206a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180506%2Flarge%2Fa1206a.gif&h=c4d4c7b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■解放軍戰機升空攔截無人機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180506/large/a1206b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180506%2Flarge%2Fa1206b.gif&h=4a5bc051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■涉事的固定翼無人機。<br />\n<br />\n河北唐山4名男子早前遙控一架無人機在礦區高空航拍，其間被解放軍雷達發現，軍方出動兩架戰機升空攔截，4人當場被拘捕。當局指飛行地點距離北京僅140多公里，多個民航航班受干擾被迫修改航線，導致延誤及經濟損失，更嚴重影響首都空防安全。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4男子遭軍警拘捕<br />\n<br />\n涉案人士包括在某技術公司任職的唐姓男子及北京一間航空公司3名員工，4人皆沒有無人機飛行執照，事先也沒有申請空域。今年2月7日，他們在唐山市操控一架油電混合動力無人機，為中國製的獵鷹-33，價值50萬元人民幣（約62萬港元），在礦區1,000米高空航拍。起飛不久即被解放軍中部戰區雷達發現。<br />\n<br />\n因當地有不少軍事基地，軍方下令兩架戰機升空攔截，發現是固定翼無人機後，當局又派地面部隊到事發地搜查，發現頭頂天空出現空軍戰機，於是馬上降落無人機，準備逃離，但軍警已趕到逮捕他們。<br />\n<br />\n警方指4人已觸犯刑法，涉嫌危害公共安全罪被捕，將面臨法律制裁。有網民讚揚解放軍「空防實力強大」，亦有網民質疑有沒有必要如此大陣仗，起飛戰機攔截，「不如發射防空導彈，直接擊落算了」！<br />\n<br />\n中國軍網  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n廣州淫官受賄　免費嫖妓200次<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n被官二代呃7年感情　揚州「甄嬛」展開絕地反擊"},{"pid":"697cd1675fd2fa6d75d984b7bc7f9b5851d6b992","tid":655108,"uid":24345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:28:06.000Z","msg":"防部無人機都可以對空防實力打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贏"},{"pid":"bca6ce089c030377172e1c625553145647300989","tid":655108,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:31:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e43be529f36ddc8771b0f15da79be54296c69fc7","tid":655108,"uid":150881,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:34:41.000Z","msg":"我有興趣上一則多啲"},{"pid":"e8fd9cc2b5d78f96d359d9fbba332609f51404f4","tid":655108,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用架戰機打無人機? 認真 喵撚準未?"},{"pid":"98379f10ae2a1b0725ce384ff3f31e8baceb4d3c","tid":655108,"uid":10533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:25:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廣州淫官受賄　免費嫖妓200次<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個吸引啲"}]}